# Icons Distribution

This directory contains the compiled and normalized icon data.

## Structure (WIP)

```
dist/
├── <package>/
│   ├── package.json
│   ├── <group>/
│   │   ├── <group>.group.json
│   │   ├── <icon>.json
│   │   ├── <icon>.svg
```

## Maintenance

This directory is committed to git to serve as a reliable source of truth for icon data.
Do not manually edit files in this directory; they should be generated by build scripts.
